  "blurb": "The completed, fully-furnished show villa of an exclusive hillside collection above Layan Beach — a three-plus-one-bedroom sea-view home that frames the Andaman through walls of glass, with a private 13-metre infinity pool on its terrace. Move-in ready across 921 m² of built area on a 749 m² plot. ฿120,000,000.",
  "detail": "The completed show villa of an exclusive hillside collection set above Layan Beach, on Phuket's prestigious north-west coast — delivered fully furnished and ready to move into. Three bedrooms plus a fourth flexible room open onto panoramic Andaman Sea views, framed through floor-to-ceiling glass and reflected in a private infinity pool that runs the length of the terrace.\n\nThe home offers 921 m² of built area on a 749 m² plot, in a contemporary architecture of crisp white planes, warm timber ceilings and natural stone. Open-plan living and dining flow directly to the pool deck, where a 13.00 × 4.00 m infinity pool with a 1.30 m depth sits against the sea horizon. Every room is turnkey — furnished, styled and equipped, with designer kitchen and bathrooms.\n\nLayan is one of Phuket's most sought-after enclaves — a quiet, green setting minutes from Layan and Bang Tao beaches, Laguna's golf and the island's best dining. Completed in 2026 and available now, the villa suits both an immediate move-in and a strong rental investment. Offered freehold or leasehold.",
